# Lightify - Custom Neon Signs

A modern website for a custom neon sign business. Lightify specializes in creating bespoke neon signs for businesses and personal use.

## Core Features
- Custom neon sign design and manufacturing.
- Portfolio showcase of previous neon sign projects.
- Pricing information for various neon LED configurations.
- Contact for custom quotes.

## Key Pages
- [Home](https://lightify.ro/): Introduction to Lightify and featured neon signs.
- [Portfolio](https://lightify.ro/portofoliu-semne-neon): A collection of neon sign projects.
- [Pricing](https://lightify.ro/preturi-neon-led): Details on costs and options for neon signs.
- [About Us](https://lightify.ro/despre-noi): Information about the company and its story.
- [Contact](https://lightify.ro/contact): Form and details to get in touch for orders.
- [Why Lightify](https://lightify.ro/de-ce-lightify): Benefits of choosing Lightify for neon signs.

## Contact Information
- Website: https://lightify.ro
- Contact Page: https://lightify.ro/contact
